{"tid":1574779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城online] 人人都可以喺現場做到嘅職業","createTime":"2019-09-16T14:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T19:04:04.000Z","uid":54564,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e73def7385c24d5f6cce5ca56a65d38594fff219","tid":1574779,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:44:24.000Z","msg":"今日主要想同大家推廣下新職業<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>「翻譯師」</strong></span>同簡單教下點做<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「製石兵」</span></strong><br />\n其實之前都開過post講過下翻譯師<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇諗過R下外國記者吹水<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550982</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然話<span style=\"color: orange;\">「自己香城自己救」</span>，但係相信大家都唔否認<span style=\"color: orange;\">借助下外國勢力</span>會令呢場戰役打得更舒服<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">［未FC］</span></span></strong>根據身邊有做傳媒呢行嘅消息，<br />\n自<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8月起多咗好多外國媒體特登派記者留喺香城都做新聞做採訪</strong></span> (我哋已經成功吸引咗全世界勢力關注)，<br />\n<br />\n而呢d外國勢力記者因為唔識得廣東話所以 <span style=\"color: violet;\">［特登想搵大學生／傳理系學生幫手跟住呢班記者幫手做翻譯+帶路+解釋現場發生緊咩事］</span>(我都係咁聽返嚟fc唔到)<br />\n<br />\n而我都相信唔係每一個媒體都會搵到本地人去幫佢哋手，所以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成日都見唔少外媒係唔知現場發生緊咩事</span></span> (之前嗰post都講過)<br />\n<br />\n所以我建議所有發夢嘅香城人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好怕醜，多d去同外媒接觸下</span></span>，溝通下，傾下計甚至做訪問<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如實咁同佢哋講下點解大家要咁做／現場發生緊乜事</strong></span><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: large;\">就算佢當下唔信你，起碼知道咗大家點諗，點解要企出嚟先，咁樣佢落筆嗰時都可以考慮下寫唔寫呢個point</span></em><br />\n<br />\n(我相信唔少近唔貼香城online 最新patch嘅外國玩家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">唔知咩係fucking 幫<br />\n點解要c鳥fucking 幫, <br />\n甚至唔知點解要破壞萬惡黨鐵</span>)<br />\n<br />\n雖然未必講完就令佢哋即時理解我哋，但起碼叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>多個機會比佢哋知道我哋點解咁做</strong></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>手足從來都唔會好似垃圾<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲廢老</span>咁「無端端搞破壞＋無差別傷害人」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算報我哋都唔應該話場運動走向<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">UGLY</span></span></strong>, 而係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>GLORY</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>同場加映:</strong> </span><br />\n喺online入面見到<span style=\"color: violet;\">多咗好多新入行手足</span>會嘗試去做後勤幫手製造遠程磚石武器 (好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n大家記住個重點係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「要一隻手揸得曬舊磚石」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">(太大舊會太重掟唔出, 太細舊掟中咗都冇傷害)</span></span></em><br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>要點樣製造? </ins></em><br />\n<br />\n1. 見有唔少<span style=\"color: gold;\">課金玩家</span>會用<span style=\"color: red;\">錘仔/鐵通</span>去打碎d石<br />\n2. 亦都有<span style=\"color: violet;\">暴力玩家</span>會拎起舊磚<span style=\"color: red;\">一嘢掟落個石壆到撞碎佢</span><br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無課玩家</span></strong>可以嘗試下<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用兩舊磚墊底，放一舊長磚喺上面，然後拎一舊磚用角位撞斷上面舊長磚</span></strong>（大槪１／３左右個SIZE就差唔多） (如下圖, 小畫家水準係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ztswv5P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZtswv5P.png&h=e9482c22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然如果有更好方法都歡迎同路人提出+教埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[i]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">p.s. 記得帶返對手套保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>/i]"},{"pid":"6519be2bead3d5cd850851e1c038bc01ae115c33","tid":1574779,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"